{"tid":1610130,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（人手置頂）超重要！！！急診室求診須知","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:51:21.000Z","uid":240344,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1d92a3130b33442af6e432ccf2b040902046ce7a","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"以下是代TG朋友出Post<br />\n<br />\n急診室求診須知<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我明白係狗屋個48個鐘一定會非常難挨，入去到一定講要睇醫生，請相信香港仲有班有良知既醫護人員，而以下係去到急診室你要知既事。<br />\n<br />\n醫護會同你做分流，而除左同護士講表面損傷（但唔好講比狗咬、中槍個啲）<br />\n以下既情況醫生都不能夠輕易放你出院：<br />\n<br />\n癲癇症狀、心臟問題、腦出血（要睇表面徵狀，或scan睇下你係未真係有事）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以講就係咁多<br />\n<br />\n最後 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n天佑我城"},{"pid":"e1ac528a8356fcc03963128327c1eb0685e639e3","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"5e7d6bf3d693af566f98ac9949909d4f3148c93f","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"410e051a2c8c7ba0ba13b2fe32ed5efc60dfd2b9","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"cce8b1fd59dcf0242f0853d2e92b6d389c6b7e7a","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"10a8280c3693117dbe0e1f863f9539a0d23f4d19","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"ded52625105938289f505de407b37296262d4c95","tid":1610130,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6414cf273cd3c4e0a861497913e03672012a277a","tid":1610130,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:28:16.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"